snippet.title: MARLENE RELEASE TRAILER - VR Horror game.
snippet.description:
Take on the role of Ewan as he investigates his estranged sisters remote cottage and surroundings to uncover the truth about his niece Marlene's disappearance. Complete tasks and solve puzzles to progress this supernatural horror story in VR.
Available now at:
https://uzigames.co.uk
http://store.steampowered.com/app/536530
https://www.humblebundle.com/store/marlene
